AUDIT LOG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Create persistent audit system.

Audit fields:

- id
- actor_user_id
- actor_email
- action
- resource_type
- resource_id
- result
- ip_address
- user_agent
- metadata
- created_at

Audit these actions:

- login success
- login failure
- logout
- token refresh
- risk halt
- risk resume
- scheduler job create
- scheduler job run
- scheduler job delete
- IoT action requested
- content approval
- content publish request
- backtest run
- optimization run
- promotion check
- admin user action

Required endpoints:

GET /api/admin/audit-logs

Query params:
- action
- actor_email
- resource_type
- limit

GET /api/admin/users

POST /api/admin/users

PATCH /api/admin/users/{user_id}

DELETE /api/admin/users/{user_id}

Rules:

- Only admin can manage users.
- Do not permanently delete current authenticated admin.
- Prefer deactivate over hard delete.
- Never return password hashes.

